<br>
<h2>River Description</h2>
<p>
This designated Wild and Scenic River&nbsp;flows through a deep basalt canyon in the remote
desert country of southeast Oregon.&nbsp;
</p> <br>
<div style='clear:both'>
<div><b>StreamTeam Status: </b>Not Verified</div>
